{
  "stem": "20405.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't remember how many or why they took. 100, 300, 400 I don't know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the reason, because they put us to open some trenches, big trenches in the same lot of the crematoriums, was about two or three big ones.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can tell you maybe 100 feet, maybe more, with 50, 60 feet large, because they were waiting all the Jewish from Hungary.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took some Jewish from Hungary before, but I don't know why those Jewish, they couldn't take her away, was political?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Think-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And was all the-- those rich Jewish from Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We know because they were Jewish, because we found a lot of gold, and diamonds, et cetera, et cetera from those people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And because [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] in a few words, they killed them about 30,000, I can tell you, in about two weeks, three weeks, 30,000 of the Hungarian people.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And those strangers, what they did, they put some wood in the bottom and some gasoline.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all this wood and the gasoline was burning all the time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from the gas chamber, working 24 hours a day, taking all those dead bodies and threw them right in those trenches.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were burning this time because the ovens was not enough to burn so many people in so long-- in so little time.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And it happened to work me night time with that kind of cold, et cetera, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's so many things to say, but I cannot say it anymore.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know what-- how it happened over there, three beautiful Hungarian girls, young, beautiful Hungarian girls, they didn't want to go into the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They-- I don't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was over there an officer, SS.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
